FOUR YEARS AGO

234
00:23:40,000 --> 00:23:44,250
We promise to bring your farm
even greater happiness and abundance.

235
00:23:44,333 --> 00:23:46,666
You make wonderful coffee,

236
00:23:46,750 --> 00:23:50,833
but your current distribution method
doesn't do it justice. It's a waste.

237
00:23:50,916 --> 00:23:51,916
So, here's our plan.

238
00:23:52,000 --> 00:23:53,125
Sorry, not interested.

239
00:23:53,208 --> 00:23:56,041
Wait a second,
I haven't told you anything yet.

240
00:23:56,125 --> 00:24:00,083
We can distribute your coffee
at a price you can agree with, and…

241
00:24:04,375 --> 00:24:06,833
I'm not doing this for the money.

242
00:24:08,500 --> 00:24:10,750
That's not what I meant.

243
00:24:10,833 --> 00:24:11,666
Go home.

244
00:24:12,458 --> 00:24:13,958
Please, let me finish.

245
00:24:14,458 --> 00:24:15,666
Actually, I--

246
00:24:15,750 --> 00:24:16,708
Go home.

247
00:24:17,833 --> 00:24:19,333
I'm done listening.

248
00:24:20,166 --> 00:24:21,083
Please wait.

249
00:24:21,166 --> 00:24:22,833
I'm begging you.

250
00:24:23,625 --> 00:24:25,000
Please hear me out.

251
00:24:32,083 --> 00:24:33,708
My late wife and I

252
00:24:35,083 --> 00:24:37,375
spent 40 years building up this farm.

253
00:24:38,500 --> 00:24:40,625
I don't plan on changing a thing.

254
00:24:43,083 --> 00:24:44,291
My answer won't change.

255
00:24:45,083 --> 00:24:46,291
Sorry, but give up.

256
